				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">How long is a "very long time"?
<br />
<br />What you are describing involves shifting a 72-byte buffer by a distance of 1 byte. The following takes fewer than 1100 cycles per my count, and would take even fewer if unrolled:
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; ldx #0<br />@loop:<br />&nbsp; lda buffer+1,x<br />&nbsp; sta buffer,x<br />&nbsp; inx<br />&nbsp; cpx #71<br />&nbsp; bcc @loop<br /></div></div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
